SummaryContractMilestoneForm is a SummaryForm
    title is "ContractMilestoneInformation"
    Layout
        two column
            Contract
            Contract.Name
        single column
            Name
            Description
            MilestoneDate
            Quantity
            Rate
            Amount
            PercentComplete
            CompletionStatus
                display as text
            PersonResponsible
        paragraph
            paragraph
                NumberOfDaysToFirstAlert
                    label is "FirstAlert-Yellow-Is"
                text of "DaysBeforeDueDate."
            paragraph
                NumberOfDaysToSecondAlert
                    label is "SecondAlert-Red-Is"
                text of "DaysBeforeDueDate."
        visible when (CommentsExist)
            list is ContractMilestoneComment set.ContractMilestoneCommentsPrint
